{
  "stem": "5654.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because by the time we were, let's say, 15, 16, we had lived like somebody who was 25 with all what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it's normal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there we-- it was not a pleasant place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to sleep in-- we used to sleep on the-- in-- it was a school, so we slept in-- in the classroom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The classroom was divided into-- into sections, you know, like 2 meters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a board and the straw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to sleep on straw on the floor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were given blankets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we stayed there, I think, for about three or four weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not being used as a school, no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, that-- that school became so crowded, they decide to move the old-- the ones who arrived earlier, to another school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other school was called-- it was called a [INAUDIBLE] also in Geneva, not very far from-- from where that was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, it had a big playground, so it was much better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, again, we slept on the- on the floor, on the board, and in the-- in the classrooms.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I can remember in 1943, it was Rosh Hashanah arrived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were trying to get a-- story was like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were trying to get--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah...",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ok",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
